title: Blue Jays clinch AL East with 15-2 win over Orioles
text:
> Sports Blue Jays clinch AL East with 15-2 win over Orioles Baltimore Orioles starting pitcher Miguel Gonzalez walks off the field after being relieved in the fourth inning in the first baseball game of a doubleheader against the Toronto Blue Jays, Wednesday, Sept. 30, 2015, in Baltimore.
